name: Keyboard Practice (Liki Games)
description:
Challenge yourself with the most score for typing in 1 minute and beat your high score

Keyboard Practice will get you familiar with your keyboard and help you to type fast by challenging you to beat your high score in 60 seconds.

In a battle against time, you are to type as fast as you can to beat your scores and create a new high score. 

Try typing as fast as you can to beat your high score.

Practice makes perfect, challenge yourself everyday on typing fast and try to beat your scores everyday.

This game also contains a Free Mode with a timer. The timer is not useful as it is not used to determine the time the game needs to stop, but you can view it to know how much time you're spending and how much score you get at a particular time and make improvement to defeat time when you next you play Time Mode.
